Package: kdegift
Version: 0.7.0
Revision: 1
Source: http://ricardis.ricardis.tudelft.nl/~bastiaan/%n/%n-%v.tar.bz2
Source-MD5: 
Patch: %f.patch
SourceDirectory: %n-0.7
BuildDepends: kdelibs3-ssl-dev | kdelibs3-dev, dlcompat-dev, libart2, qt3-dev, xfree86, dlcompat
Depends: kdelibs3-ssl-shlibs | kdelibs3-shlibs, dlcompat-shlibs, libart2-shlibs, qt3-shlibs, libpng3-shlibs, xfree86-shlibs, dlcompat-shlibs
Provides: gift-frontend
Recommends: gift, gift-fasttrack
SetCXXFLAGS: -Os -g
ConfigureParams: --mandir='${prefix}/share/man' --with-qt-dir=%p --with-qt-includes=%p/include/qt --with-qt-libraries=%p/lib --with-extra-includes=%p/include
CompileScript: <<
  mv INSTALL INSTALL.txt
  ./autogen.sh
  ./configure %c
  make
  <<

DocFiles: AUTHORS COPYING ChangeLog README TODO
Description: A KDE frontend for giFT
DescDetail: <<
The program builds on the work done by Robert Wittams on his Kadeau. The front end look about the same and is reused as much as possible. The back-end has been rewritten mostly. Searches that give a lot of results back are very slow at the moment.

Features:

 * Comfortable interface
 * Multiple searches
<<
